quran[21]{c,v,t}:
  4,114,"MoЖґЖґere alaa e ko heewi e yeewtere maЙ“Й“e nden, si wanaa on yamirЙ—o sadaka, maa moЖґЖґere maa moЖґЖґiЕ‹tingol hakkunde yimЙ“e Й“en. Kala waЙ—irЙ—o Й—um Й—aЙ“Й“ugol welayee Alla, arma Men Okka mo njoЙ“di mawndi"
  4,115,"Kala on lunndiiЙ—o NulaaЙ—o on Й“aawo nde paawal ngal Й“anngani mo, o jokki ko wanaa laawol gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en, Men HucciЕ‹tinay mo e kon ko o hucciti, Men Naadoya mo Jahannanma, nge bonii ruttorde"
  4,116,"Pellet, Alla Yawtantaa kafidugol Mo e goЙ—Й—um, Himo Yawtana ko jaasi Й—um wonannde on Mo O Muuyi. Kala on kafiduЙ—o Alla e goЙ—Й—um, gomЙ—ii o majjii majjere woЙ—Й—iinde"
  4,117,"ЖЃe alaa e rewude ko woori Alla, si wanaa [sanamuuji] rewЙ—inaaЙ—i, Й“e alaa e rewude si wanaa seytaane sanndalЙ—iinЙ—o"
  4,118,"Alla HuЙ—ii ndu, ndu wi'i : \"Ma mi jogitoyo e jeyaaЙ“e maa Й“en geЙ“al farlaangal"
  4,119,"ma mi majjinoyЙ“e, ma mi yelinoyЙ“e, ma mi yamiroyЙ“e, ma Й“e taЖґu noppi neemoraaЙ—i Й—in, ma mi yamirЙ“e, ma Й“e waylu tagu Alla ngun !\". Kala jogitiiЙ—o seytaane giЙ—o ko woori Alla, gomЙ—ii o hayrii hayrere Й“anngunde"
  4,120,"Himo foda Й“e himo yelina Й“e, seytaane fodaali Й“e si wanaa hodo"
  4,121,"ЖЃen Й—on wemoolorde maЙ“Й“e nden ko Jahannama, Й“e heЙ“irtaa nge daЙ—irde"
  4,122,"ЖЃen gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“e golli golle moЖґЖґe, aray Men Naada Й“e Aljannaaji Й—i no ila e ley majji canЙ—i : ko Й“e duumotooЙ“e nder ton poomaa. Fodoore Alla nde ko goonga. Ko hommbo Й“uri Alla goongude konngol ? @Corrected"
  4,123,"Wonaali ko yelaaji mon Й—in wanaa yelaaji jomЙ“e Defte Й“en. Kala golluЙ—o bone o yoЙ“ete Й—um, o heЙ“anoytaake ko woori Alla giЙ—o wanaa ballo"
  4,124,"Kala golluЙ—o immorde e moЖґЖґi Й—in, fota ko gorko maa ko debbo, hara ko o gomЙ—inЙ—o, Й“en Й—on naatay Aljanna Й“e tooГ±etaake yeru gurun [tamaro]"
  4,125,"Alaa Й“urЙ—o moЖґЖґude diina haa hewti on jebbilЙ—o yeeso mun ngon Alla, hara ko o moЖґЖґinЙ—o, o rewi laawol Ibraahiima ruuЙ—iiЙ—o. Alla Jogitike Ibraahiima giЙ—o"
  4,126,Ko Alla Woodani kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi. Alla Laatike HuЙ“indiiЙ—o kala huunde
  4,127,"HiЙ“e lamdo maa fii rewЙ“e Й“en, maaku : \"Alla no saggitude on fii Й“en [rewЙ“e], e kon ko jaЕ‹ngetee e dow mooЙ—on ka Deftere fii Й“en rewЙ“e wonduЙ“e, Й“en Й“e on jonnataa kon ko Й“e farlanaaa, hiЙ—on rerЙ—a fii resugol Й“e, e Й“en lo'inaaЙ“e immorde ka fayЙ“e, e nde daraЕ‹toЙ—on wonduЙ“e Й“en nunЙ—al. Kala ko huuwoton e moЖґЖґere, pellet, Alla Laatike AnnduЙ—o Й—um"
  4,128,"Si wonii debbo hulirii moodi makko suwtaade suwtaade maa Й—uurnaare, bakkaatu fawaaki Й“e nde Й“e moЖґЖґiЕ‹tinirta hakkunde maЙ“Й“e sulhu.Ko sulhu on Й“uri moЖґЖґude, pittaali Й—in tawdaama ndeereraaku.Si on moЖґЖґinii on gomЙ—ii, pellet Alla Laatike HumpitiiЙ—o ko golloton"
  4,129,"On waawataa nunЙ—ude hakkunde rewЙ“e Й“en hay si on rerЙ—ii. Wata tun on ooГ±o kala ooГ±annde, accon mo wa yowaaЙ—o. Si on moЖґЖґinii on gomЙ—ii, pellet, Alla Laatike Haforoowo HinnotooЙ—o"
  4,130,"Si Й“e sertii, Alla AlЙ—iniroyay kala maЙ“Й“e immorde e Yaajeende Makko nden. Alla Laatike YaajuЙ—o [Й“ural], Г‘eeЙ—uЙ—o"
  4,131,"Ko Alla Woodani kala ko woni ka kammuuli kon e ka leydi. GomЙ—ii Men Ahodinoke e Й“eya okkaaЙ“e Defte ado mon, e onon : \"Hulee Alla !\". Si on yeddii, pellet, ko Alla Woodani kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi. Alla Laatike Galo, YettiniiЙ—o"
  4,132,Ko Alla Woodani kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi. Alla Yonii FawtiiЙ—o
  4,133,"Si O Muuyii, O NaЙ“ay on, onon yo yimЙ“e, O Adda woЙ—Й“e goo. Alla Laatike HattanЙ—o e dow Й—um"
  4,134,"Kala tawЙ—o no faandii mbarjaari aduna, ko ka Alla mbarjaari aduna e laakara woni. Alla Laatike Nanoowo, Yi'oowo"